(5101, 315, 'excerpt', 'Our cladding works encompass both CNC and 2D options, & 3D types of cladding facades providing versatility and flexibility in design. CNC cladding allowsfor intricate and precise patterns, ideal for projects where detailed customization is desired. On the other hand, 2D cladding offers a cost-effective solution with a diverse range of design possibilities, ensuring that we can meet the aesthetic and budgetary requirements.'),
(5102, 315, '_excerpt', 'field_65d960167f8a6'),
(5103, 315, 'description', 'Elevate your building\'s exterior to a masterpiece with our <strong>facade construction &amp; design service</strong>. We don\'t just create structures; we craft iconic impressions. Our team of architects and designers blends form and function, infusing your facade with architectural elegance and contemporary flair. From sleek glass facades that reflect modernity to intricate designs that pay homage to tradition, we specialize in turning visions into striking realities. Whether it\'s a commercial skyscraper, a residential complex, or a cultural landmark, our innovative approach ensures that every facade tells a captivating story, leaving a lasting impression on all who behold it.'),
