(11362, 522, 'excerpt', 'Crafted with precision and attention to detail, our ceiling panels add a touch of elegance to any room. Choose from a wide range of styles, finishes, and customizable options to create a truly unique ceiling design that complements your decor. Whether you prefer classic sophistication or contemporary chic, our panels are designed to impress. Easy to install and maintain, they offer long-lasting beauty without the hassle.'),
(11363, 522, '_excerpt', 'field_65d960167f8a6'),
(11364, 522, 'description', 'Elevate your space with our ceiling solutions designed for both aesthetics and functionality. Opt for bulkhead ceilings to conceal utilities while adding architectural interest, available in customizable shapes and finishes. Suspended ceilings provide easy access to overhead utilities and enhance acoustic and thermal insulation, with options for tile type, grid layout, and lighting integration. PVC ceilings offer durability and low maintenance, with customizable colors, textures, and designs to suit any environment.'),
