(11418, 522, 'consultancy_accordion_content_0_description', 'Our collection of Facade Experts ceiling panels can completely transform your space. Suitable for any room in your house, including the kitchen, bathroom, and more, ceiling paneling is a great easy to maintain substitute for a painted or tiled ceiling. Available in a range of designs, including cool-toned grey wood effect and clean white gloss, these ceilings are easy to install thanks to their effective tongue and groove interlocking system. Our ceiling panels are durable, easy to install, and reasonably priced, providing an attractive finish to any space at a reasonable price.'),
