(11609, 563, 'excerpt', 'Whether you\'re aiming for a chic modern ambience, a cozy rustic retreat, or something entirely unique, our customizable design solutions, vibrant colour schemes and striking patterns to elegant finishes and textures ensure that your space captivates visitors from the moment they arrive.'),
(11610, 563, '_excerpt', 'field_65d960167f8a6'),
(11611, 563, 'description', 'Let\'s talk for a moment about how to approach the consulting aspect of designing and building a <strong>hotel, restaurant,villa cabana, or cafe</strong>. To make sure your designs are achievable, it is always an excellent decision to consult with specialists in design. Facade Experts may help you with the project\'s mechanical, electrical, and plumbing components after you\'ve completed your basic designs. Not only can they draw out the pipe system, but they can also offer advice on how energy will be carried into the structure. In essence, Facade Experts may take care of some of the more subtle aspects of approving the overall design for your project.\r\n\r\nSeeking the advice of a structural engineering expert can provide you a second opinion regarding the project\'s architectural goals, including the selection of materials and their suitability for the intended design. We can also provide you with advice regarding the project\'s plan, including whether or not the dining area, entryway, and bedrooms may all be made more efficient.'),
